ted sales===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Chart \n!Amount\n|-\n|''Oricon'' physical sales<ref name=\"OricSubsc\">{{cite web | title=\u30aa\u30ea\u30b3\u30f3\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0\u60c5\u5831\u30b5\u30fc\u30d3\u30b9\u300cyou\u5927\u6a39\u300d | url=http://ranking.oricon.co.jp | work=[[Oricon]] | accessdate=March 17, 2013}} (subscription only)</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|26,000<!--26,096-->\n|}\n\n==Personnel==\n\nCredits for ''Square One'' adapted from the liner booklet.<ref>{{cite video |people=Verbal, Taku Takahashi |date=March 14, 2012 |title=Square One |medium=Album liner booklet |language=Japanese |publisher=Rhythm Zone |location=Tokyo, Japan}}</ref>\n\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n* Masaji Asakawa \u2013 executive production for Artimage\n* Junji Chiba \u2013 keyboards <small>(track 6)</small>\n* Ryuhei Chiba \u2013 executive supervision\n* Kurt \"KC\" Common \u2013 narrator <small>(track 1)</small>\n* El Poco Maro \u2013 programming <small>(track 16)</small>\n* Taiki Fudanotsuji \u2013 assistant recording engineer <small>(track 4, 7, 15, 18\u201319)</small>\n* Yosuke Fukui \u2013 lyrics <small>(track 13)</small>, music composition <small>(track 13)</small>\n* [[:ja:\u798f\u5c71\u77e5\u6c99|Chisa Fukuyama]] \u2013 narrator <small>(track 4, 7)</small>\n* Stewart Hawkes \u2013 mastering <small>(track 1\u20136, 8\u201311, 13\u201314, 16\u201319)</small>\n* Shinji Hayashi \u2013 executive supervision\n* Mitsunori Ikeda \u2013  guitars <small>(track 9)</small>, mixing <small>(track 2\u20133, 5\u20136, 8\u201311, 13\u201314, 16\u201318)</small>, programming <small>(track 1\u20133, 5\u201311, 13\u201314, 17\u201319)</small>, recording engineer <small>(track 2\u20133, 5\u20136, 8\u201311, 13\u201314, 16\u201318)</small>\n* Osamu \"Shu\" Imamoto \u2013 recording engineer <small>(track 2\u20133, 5, 8\u20139, 11, 14 17)</small>\n* Hiroshi Inagaki \u2013 general producer\n* Koji Kage \u2013 lyrics <small>(track 13)</small>\n* Naoki Kakuta \u2013 recording engineer <small>(t