en]]<ref group=\"nb\">The event ran under different names such as the Grand Prix (1992/1993\u20132000/2001 and 2004/2005\u20132009/2010), LG Cup (2001/2002\u20132003/2004), World Open (2010/2011) and Haikou World Open (2011/2012)</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1997 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1998 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2002 LG Cup (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2003 LG Cup (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:thistle;\"|[[2004 Grand Prix (snooker)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2005 Grand Prix (snooker)|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2006 Grand Prix (snooker)|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2007 Grand Prix (snooker)|RR]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2009 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| {{nowrap|[[Players Championship Grand Final]]<ref group=\"nb\">The event ran under a different name as the Players Tour Championship Grand Finals (2010/2011\u20132012/2013)</ref>}}\n| colspan=\"18\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|DNQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|DNQ\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[China Open (snooker)|China Open]]<ref group=\"nb\" name=\"CHN\">The event ran under a different name as the China International (1997/1998\u20131998/1999)</ref>\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|NR\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2000 China Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2002 China Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2007 China Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[World Snooker Championship|World Championship]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1999 World Snooker Championship|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2003 World Snooker Championship|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2004 World Snooker Championship|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:yellow;\" |[[2005 World Snooker Championship|SF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2007 World Snooker Championship|2R]]\n